<inglise> Regulation (EEC) No 1031/75 of the Commission of 17 April 1975 defining the event in which the subsidy in respect of cotton seeds becomes due and payable </inglise>
<eesti> KOMISJONI M&Auml;&Auml;RUS (EM&Uuml;) nr 1031/75, millega m&auml;&auml;ratletakse juht, mil tuleb maksta subsiidiumi puuvillaseemnete eest 17. aprill 1975 </eesti>
<inglise> THE COMMISSION OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES, </inglise>
<eesti> EUROOPA &Uuml;HENDUSTE KOMISJON, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Economic Community; </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa Majandus&uuml;henduse asutamislepingut; </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation (EEC) No 1516/71 (1) of 12 July 1971 introducing a system of subsidies for cotton seeds, and in particular Article 1 (5) thereof; </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 12. juuli 1971. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 1516/71, (1) millega kehtestatakse puuvillaseemnete subsiidiumide s&uuml;steem, eriti selle artikli 1 l&otilde;iget 5, </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas Article 4 (2) of Council Regulation (EEC) No 1134/68 (2) of 30 July 1968 laying down rules for the implementation of Regulation (EEC) No 653/68 (3) on conditions for alterations to the value of the unit of account used for the common agricultural policy, provides that for transactions carried out pursuant to provisions on the common agricultural policy the sums owed by a Member State or a duly authorized body, expressed in national currency and representing amounts fixed in units of account are to be paid on the basis of the relationship between the unit of account and the national currency which obtained at the time when the transaction or part transaction was carried out; </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: n&otilde;ukogu 30. juuli 1968. aasta m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 1134/68 (2) (millega s&auml;testatakse &uuml;hise p&otilde;llumajanduspoliitika raames kasutatava arvestus&uuml;hiku v&auml;&auml;rtuse muutmise tingimusi kohta antud m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 653/68 (3) rakenduseeskirjad) artikli 4 l&otilde;ikes 2 s&auml;testatakse, et &uuml;hise p&otilde;llumajanduspoliitika s&auml;tete kohaselt sooritatud tehingute eest makstakse omav&auml;&auml;ringus v&auml;ljendatud ja arvestus&uuml;hikutes kindlaksm&auml;&auml;ratud m&auml;&auml;rasid esindavad summad, mida v&otilde;lgneb liikmesriik v&otilde;i volitatud asutus, arvestus&uuml;hiku ja omav&auml;&auml;ringu vahelise suhte alusel, mis kehtis tehingu v&otilde;i selle osa sooritamise ajal; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas Article 6 of Regulation (EEC) No 1134/68 provides that the time when a transaction is carried out is to be considered to be the date on which occurs the event, as defined by Community rules, or, in the absence of and pending adoption of such rules, by the rules of the Member State concerned, in which the amount involved in the transaction becomes due and payable; </inglise>
<eesti> m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 1134/68 artiklis 6 s&auml;testatakse, et tehingu sooritamise ajaks peetakse kuup&auml;eva, mil ilmneb asjaolu, mis on m&auml;&auml;ratletud &uuml;henduse eeskirjades v&otilde;i nende eeskirjade puudumisel v&otilde;i kuni nende vastuv&otilde;tmiseni asjaomase liikmesriigi eeskirjades ning mis annab &otilde;iguse tehinguga h&otilde;lmatud summa saamiseks; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the event in which the subsidy for cotton seeds becomes due and payable occurs at the time when the cotton is produced; whereas, however, it is very difficult to establish the exact date of production for a given lot; </inglise>
<eesti> juht, mil tuleb maksta subsiidiumi puuvillaseemnete eest, on puuvilla tootmise ajal; siiski on v&auml;ga raske kindlaks teha asjaomase partii t&auml;pset tootmiskuup&auml;eva; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas experience has shown that production of cotton is almost entirely completed during the month of October of each year at the latest; whereas in order to ensure uniform operation of the system of subsidies, the conversion rate to be used to calculate the amounts of the subsidy in the relevant national currency should be the rate applicable at the end of that month; </inglise>
<eesti> kogemused on n&auml;idanud, et peaaegu kogu puuvillatootmine l&otilde;ppeb hiljemalt iga aasta oktoobri jooksul; subsiidiumide s&uuml;steemi &uuml;htse toimimise tagamiseks peaks subsiidiumim&auml;&auml;rade omav&auml;&auml;ringusse arvutamiseks kasutatav &uuml;mberarvestuskurss olema k&otilde;nealuse kuu l&otilde;pul kohaldatav kurss; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the measures provided for in this Regulation are in accordance with the Opinion of the Management Committee for Oils and Fats, </inglise>
<eesti> k&auml;esolevas m&auml;&auml;ruses etten&auml;htud meetmed on koosk&otilde;las &otilde;li- ja rasvaturu korralduskomitee arvamusega, </eesti>
<inglise> HAS ADOPTED THIS REGULATION: </inglise>
<eesti> ON VASTU V&Otilde;TNUD K&Auml;ESOLEVA M&Auml;&Auml;RUSE. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> The event within the meaning of Article 6 of Regulation (EEC) No 1134/68 in which the subsidy for cotton seeds becomes due and payable shall be considered to have occurred on 1 November following the beginning of each marketing year. </inglise>
<eesti> Juhuna m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 1134/68 artikli 6 t&auml;henduses, mil tuleb maksta subsiidiumi puuvillaseemnete eest, k&auml;sitatakse iga turustusaasta algusele j&auml;rgneval 1. novembril. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall enter into force on 1 August 1975. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus j&otilde;ustub 1. augustil 1975. aastal. </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall be binding in its entirety and directly applicable in all Member States. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus on tervikuna siduv ja vahetult kohaldatav k&otilde;ikides liikmesriikides. </eesti>
<inglise> Done at Brussels, 17 April 1975. </inglise>
<eesti> Br&uuml;ssel, 17. aprill 1975 </eesti>
